cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the use of computer vision and machine learning for mobile disease diagnostics in crops. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of crowdsourcing, which suggests a possible fit with cs.CY (Computers and Society). The use of machine learning also suggests a possible fit with cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the mention of the platform www.PlantVillage.org suggests a possible fit with cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
